&lt;h2 id=&#34;pi-hole&#34;&gt;Pi-hole&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I have installed Pi-hole on multiple devices to create a redundant and fault-tolerant network setup. By running multiple instances, I ensure that ad-blocking and DNS resolution remain active even if one device goes offline or restarts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
